} else {
    context.state.init.push(statements.length === 1 ? statements[0] : b.block(statements));
}
```

When there are async values, a `$.async` call is made. The async_ids are the memoized identifiers (like `$0`, `$1`). The async function parameter list would include `$$anchor` (context.state.node) and the async_ids.

