{/snippet}

{@render child()}
```

Here, `value` is from `{:then value}` and is rendered inside a nested snippet `inner` via `{@render inner(value)}`. The `value` is passed as a render tag argument.

Actually wait, this isn't what the issue is about either. The "without explicitly declaring it in the snippet parameters" means the snippet parameters don't include the variable.

